summary:
- **New Securities Issuance**: 12,625,434 ordinary fully paid shares (GG8) to be quoted, resulting from conversion of performance rights (GG8AD) on 02/07/2025.  
- **Consideration**: Conversion of vested performance rights from Distilled Analytics Pty Ltd acquisition (September 2024), implied value **A$0.385 per share**.  
- **Post-Issuance Capital**: Total ordinary shares on issue **640,555,981**; unquoted securities include options and residual performance rights (details in announcement).  

No material impact on liquidity or capital structure (existing class issuance).
